Kumi
================================================================================


Build system for C++

Pretty much WIP


REQUIREMENTS
------------

- Clang 21+
- Clang-format 21+
- uv (conan 2+, gersemi 19+)


BUILD PROJECT
-------------

- Create a virtual environment (e.g., with uv) and install dependencies:
    - `uv venv`
    - `uv pip install conan gersemi`

- Build the project:
    - Run `make`
    - To build the release build: `make BUILD_TYPE=Release`


